review.reviewBody: super good! pad thai was a little different but the stirfry was great! big portion

Second time ordering from this restaurant and this time didnt meet expectation from the first. The pad thai was very dry, overcooked, and only had 2/3 peices of chicken.  Very bad experience and wont be ordering again.
My meal was cooked to perfection this time and I'm so grateful. Thank you for Tina and the entire Thai town.
